divs: sighting details i was sitting in a supermarket cafe when i looked up into the blue sky and saw a mustard yellow\dark gold parafoil shaped object moving slowly across the sky from east to south at an elevation of about 30 degrees. as it moved it changed shape gently and became more ringlike but kept rippling. it very much reminded me of the morphing ufo that i and my children had seen in torquay last year. i was talking on my mobile and said "i can see a ufo!". the young man at the table next to me looked up at it but seemed unimpressed. i rushed out of the cafe to the supermarket carpark to get a better look at the object but it was receding into the distance so very little more detail was visible and it then disappeared behind the treeline.

Summary: Yellow morphing UFO over Newton Abbot, Devon UK.
